<div class="wrapper wrapper_padding clearfix">
    <div class="col-1 about homepage_content">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <hr>
        <p>
            I've just graduated from one of Europe's leading coding boot camps -
            <a href="http://makersacademy.com" target="_blank">Makers Academy</a>, in London. I aspire to become a full stack junior web developer, working in the city that I love, Bristol.
        </p>
        <p>
            This is a portfolio blog I designed from scratch in Ruby on Rails in order to showcase some of my web development projects and graphic designs. You can read in detail about this web app here: <a href="https://pure-citadel-12169.herokuapp.com/projects/personal-portfolio-and-blog-app" target="_blank">Personal Rails Portfolio</a>
        </p>
        <p>
          Please feel free to contact me by sending me a message either directly, or using the contact link above. You can also view my twitter, linkedin and github profiles, by clicking on the links below right.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-2 homepage_content">
        <h2>Latests Blog Posts</h2>
        <hr>

        <% @posts.each do |post| %>
        <h3>
            <a href="#"><%= link_to post.title, post %></a>
        </h3>
        <p class="date"><%= post.created_at.strftime("%A, %b %d")%></p>
        <% end %>
    </div>

    <div class="col-3 homepage_content">
        <h2>Latest Projects</h2>
        <hr>
        <% @projects.each do |project| %>
        <h3>
            <a href="#"><%= link_to project.title, project %></a>
        </h3>
        <p class="date"><%= project.created_at.strftime("%A, %b %d")%></p>
        <% end %>
    </div>
</div>
